game.name: Barbies Fashion Boutique
game.description:
A good space for shop is available at your nearby area. And, you have immediately decided to purchase it and own a fashion boutique from there. Today is a wonderful day since extremely beautiful Barbie has come to your shop to purchase some trendy outfits. Do you help her out to find the fashionable items she loves to carry? Join Barbies Fashion Boutique game today and be ready to dress her up with a perfect outfit combined with beautiful accessories!
The best thing is that your store has a good range of items to offer to her. Give your favorite doll a lovely blue color top and match it with a blue color jean and a pair of cute shoes and handbag! You can also choose a white color shot with pink lines and a short jacket and combine it with a same color mini skirt in this html5 princess dress up game. The cute princess also looks fabulous in a top without sleeves and a blue color short bottom. 
Try to mix and match all the items as you see in the boutique until you create a fabulous dress for the ball tonight! There are multiple new clothes and decoration items available in the store. Be prepared to spot a lovely fashion boutique and select the most appropriate dresses for her! Your fine fashion abilities will definitely guide you to make her look extremely awesome. Create more exclusive and attractive outfit designs in our top dressing games for girls!
